posting_body: ['This property is listed by Wendy Legeros, licensed agent with Complete Management Services', 'Minneapolis Rental Property 4825, 2BR', '1895/month', 'ID \xad4826', 'Listing type:', 'For Rent', 'Bedrooms 2', 'Bathrooms 1.75', 'Pets Smaller pet neg.', 'with $500 deposit', 'Living Area 1011 Sq.', 'FT.', 'Deposit $500', 'Property Type: Condominium', 'Parking 1 heated parking space included', 'Location Minneapolis, MN', 'Lease Term 1 year', 'Available Immediately', 'Property Description', '1211 Lagoon Avenue #303, Minneapolis, MN 55408', 'Minneapolis Rental Property 4826, 2BR', 'Live in the heart of Uptown in this spacious 2BR condo available at Lumen on Lagoon.', 'This unit features freshly painted walls throughout, a tremendous open floor plan, wood flooring in living space, tons of light from floor to ceiling windows, large kitchen island, granite counters, stainless appliances, in unit laundry and more!', 'Located in the heart of Calhoun Square, just steps from everything Calhoun Square and Uptown have to offer including restaurants, shopping, and office spaces.', 'Non smoking unit.', ' Association dues included in the rent and cover the water/sewer & trash removal and includes 1 heated parking space.', 'Renter pays all other utilities.', 'ASSOCIATION CHARGES $100 MOVE IN FEE TO BE PAID BY TENANT.', 'Additional Features', '1 Underground parking Balcony Breakfast Bar Carpet Central Air Conditioning Controlled Access Den Dishwasher Garbage Disposal Gas Stove Hardwood Floors', 'In Unit Laundry Kitchen Island Master Bath Microwave Oven On Busline Refrigerator Stainless Steel Appliances Walking Distance To Lake']
